title: Colin Cowherd's Blazing 5: 12/15/2018
itunes:title: Colin Cowherd's Blazing 5: 12/15/2018
description:
Coming off a 4-1 week Colin gives his Blazing 5 picks from week 15 to RJ Bell of Pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio who tells him which ones the wise guys in Vegas agree with. Plus, Colin releases a special bonus pick that was not included in his Blazing 5.
